                    <span>Dry and overly technical.  As an aspiring lawyer and an armchair orator, I didn't find very much that I could readily apply to the nuts and bolts of my speech writing or delivery.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">My Ears Are In Ecstasy.</div>
